         "description":"Forecast are produced four times daily. For the WIPPS GRIB2 products, each run covers 6 days (144 hours) with 1-hourly timesteps up to 48h, 3-hourly timesteps from 51h to 120h, then 6-hourly timesteps thereafter. For the netCDF product, the longer runs are at T00Z and T12Z, and shorter runs are at T06Z and T18Z. The longer runs cover 6 days (144 hours), with 1-hourly timesteps. The shortened runs provide forecasts up to 66 hours, with hourly timesteps."
      }
